By Andile Mngxitama Thanks Apostle Michael and ECG Randwest for a powerful experience in the House of God. Indeed the God of Major 1 is a living God… And indeed you are mentored by the best…  Andile Mngxitama is the President of Black First Land First (BLF), a radical black consciousness organization. He is BLF’s City of Johannesburg Mayoral candidate for the 2021 Local Government.